## Architecture

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A[Video / Image] --> B[Face Detect (OpenCV Haar)]
    B --> C[Crop + Resize + Normalize]
    C --> D[DDAMFN Model]
    D --> E[Softmax + Top-1]
    E --> F[FastAPI /predict]
    F --> G[Streamlit Demo]
